@startuml
autonumber
actor "ATCC / Backoffice Operator" as Actor
participant ":System" as System

== Get Route Details by ID ==
activate Actor
Actor -> System : getRouteById(routeId)
activate System
note right of System: The system retrieves the route\nand its current version details.
System --> Actor : returns route details
deactivate System
deactivate Actor

== List Routes from/to Airport ==
Actor -> System : listRoutesByAirport(iataCode)
activate System
note right of System: The system retrieves all routes\nwhere the airport is the origin or destination.
System --> Actor : returns list of routes for the airport
deactivate System
deactivate Actor
@enduml
